this wetsuit not only ensures safety but is also built with environmental sustainability in mind with minimal waste production. Lightweight and foldable, it's convenient to carry along, and with a 1-year limited warranty, you can ride the blue waves worry-free. Included with every suit is a repair patch to extend its life, providing even more value for your money. Make every splash with the Blue Wave Wetsuit - your ultimate companion for cold water surfing.ONWETF_CE54"}, {"key": "ec_category", "valueString": "Wetsuits"}, {"key": "ec_rating", "valueNumber": 4.5}, {"key": "clickUri", "valueString": "/products/onwetf_ce54"}, {"key": "resultType", "valueString": "product"}, {"key": "queryPinned", "valueString": "false"}, {"key": "ec_shortdesc", "valueString": "Dive into the waves with the Blue Wave Wetsuit, designed specifically for men who want to tackle cold waters with confidence. This beginner full suit, crafted from durable and comfortable neoprene, offers optimal flexibility and cold-water protection. Featuring easy back zip access and smooth flatlock seams, you can enjoy your surf sessions without any discomfort. Certified to ISO standards, this wetsuit not only ensures safety but is also built with environmental sustainability in mind with minimal waste production. Lightweight and foldable, it's convenient to carry along, and with a 1-year limited warranty, you can ride the blue waves worry-free. Included with every suit is a repair patch to extend its life, providing even more value for your money. Make every splash with the Blue Wave Wetsuit - your ultimate companion for cold water surfing.ONWETF_CE54"}, {"key": "ec_in_stock", "valueString": "true"}, {"key": "ec_item_group_id", "valueString": "9932584288530"}, {"key": "ec_gender", "valueString": "Men"}, {"key": "ec_color", "valueString": "Blue"}, {"key": "permanentid", "valueString": "gid://shopify/ProductVariant/50674633310482"}, {"key": "excerpt", "valueString": "... , designed specifically for men who want to tackle cold waters with confidence. ... Make every splash with the Blue Wave Wetsuit - your ultimate companion for cold water surfing.ONWETF_CE54"}, {"key": "totalNumberOfChildren", "valueNumber": 6.0}, {"key": "standout", "valueString": "Budget-friendly option"}, {"key": "trade_off", "valueString": "Basic flexibility"}, {"key": "best_for", "valueString": "Beginners"}]}, {"key": "1", "valueMap": [{"key": "ec_name", "valueString": "ZenSurf Full Suit - Red / L"}, {"key": "ec_brand", "valueString": "O'Neill"}, {"key": "ec_price", "valueNumber": 299.99}, {"key": "ec_promo_price", "valueNumber": 299.99}, {"key": "ec_image", "valueString": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0910/6502/4786/files/8d486fbcd37e_bottom_right_9f239b34-f80a-43d9-8d3a-4db4185b6ce3.webp?v=1766164198"}, {"key": "ec_product_id", "valueString": "gid://shopify/ProductVariant/50674625773842"}, {"key": "ec_description", "valueString": "Experience the ultimate wave-riding adventure with ZenSurf Full Suit. Designed specifically for men who love surfing, this wetsuit offers unmatched performance in cold water. Crafted from durable, sustainable Neoprene material, it features ergonomic panels for enhanced flexibility and smooth stitching for added safety. Available in striking Black, Blue, and Red colors, each wetsuit comes with a back zip for easy wear. Engineered for long-lasting use, the suit also includes blindstitched seams for superior thermal protection. Enjoy the convenience of a travel-friendly carry bag and a repair patch, all backed by a 3-year performance warranty. Whether you're riding icy waves or paddling out on a chilly day, the ZenSurf Full Suit ensures optimal comfort and protection, making it your ideal surfing companion.ONWETF_7384"}, {"key": "ec_category", "valueString": "Wetsuits"}, {"key": "ec_rating", "valueNumber": 4.5}, {"key": "clickUri", "valueString": "/products/onwetf_7384"}, {"key": "resultType", "valueString": "product"}, {"key": "queryPinned", "valueString": "false"}, {"key": "ec_shortdesc", "valueString": "Experience the ultimate wave-riding adventure with ZenSurf Full Suit. Designed specifically for men who love surfing, this wetsuit offers unmatched performance in cold water. Crafted from durable, sustainable Neoprene material, it features ergonomic panels for enhanced flexibility and smooth stitching for added safety. Available in striking Black, Blue, and Red colors, each wetsuit comes with a back zip for easy wear. Engineered for long-lasting use, the suit also includes blindstitched seams for superior thermal protection. Enjoy the convenience of a travel-friendly carry bag and a repair patch, all backed by a 3-year performance warranty. Whether you're riding icy waves or paddling out on a chilly day, the ZenSurf Full Suit ensures optimal comfort and protection, making it your ideal surfing companion.ONWETF_7384"}, {"key": "ec_in_stock", "valueString": "true"}, {"key": "ec_item_group_id", "valueString": "9934144831762"}, {"key": "ec_gender", "valueString": "Men"}, {"key": "ec_color", "valueString": "Red"}, {"key": "permanentid", "valueString": "gid://shopify/ProductVariant/50674625773842"}, {"key": "excerpt", "valueString": "Designed specifically for men who love surfing, this wetsuit offers unmatched performance in cold water. ... optimal comfort and protection, making it your ideal surfing companion.ONWETF_7384"}, {"key": "totalNumberOfChildren", "valueNumber": 18.0}, {"key": "standout", "valueString": "Premium performance"}, {"key": "trade_off", "valueString": "Higher price point"}, {"key": "best_for", "valueString": "Serious surfers"}]}, {"key": "2", "valueMap": [{"key": "ec_name", "valueString": "WaveGuard Performance Full Suit - Black / XXL"}, {"key": "ec_brand", "valueString": "O'Neill"}, {"key": "ec_price", "valueNumber": 249.99}, {"key": "ec_promo_price", "valueNumber": 249.99}, {"key": "ec_image", "valueString": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0910/6502/4786/files/a1cd999bd5d3_bottom_left.webp?v=1766164216"}, {"key": "ec_product_id", "valueString": "gid://shopify/ProductVariant/50674630951186"}, {"key": "ec_description", "valueString": "Experience the ultimate surfing adventure with the WaveGuard Performance Full Suit. Designed for surfers who demand the best, this wetsuit combines high stretch neoprene for unmatched flexibility and a heat-retaining lining to keep you warm in cold waters. Available in sleek black or stylish blue, the chest zip ensures easy access while the protective coating and welded seams provide exceptional durability and tear resistance. Made from eco-friendly materials, it includes a carry bag and hanger for convenient portability. With ISO certification and UV resistance, the WaveGuard Full Suit is your perfect companion for every surf session. Enjoy peace of mind with a lifetime seam warranty and superior performance in every wave.ONWETF_C792"}, {"key": "ec_category", "valueString": "Wetsuits"}, {"key": "ec_rating", "valueNumber": 4.9}, {"key": "clickUri", "valueString": "/products/onwetf_c792"}, {"key": "resultType", "valueString": "product"}, {"key": "queryPinned", "valueString": "false"}, {"key": "ec_shortdesc", "valueString": "Experience the ultimate surfing adventure with the WaveGuard Performance Full Suit. Designed for surfers who demand the best, this wetsuit combines high stretch neoprene for unmatched flexibility and a heat-retaining lining to keep you warm in cold waters. Available in sleek black or stylish blue, the chest zip ensures easy access while the protective coating and welded seams provide exceptional durability and tear resistance. Made from eco-friendly materials, it includes a carry bag and hanger for convenient portability. With ISO certification and UV resistance, the WaveGuard Full Suit is your perfect companion for every surf session. Enjoy peace of mind with a lifetime seam warranty and superior performance in every wave.ONWETF_C792"}, {"key": "ec_in_stock", "valueString": "true"}, {"key": "ec_item_group_id", "valueString"